        "date": "2025-12-01T19:54:01Z",
        "message": "Update PLC4X to 0.13.1 and refactor driver usage\n\nUpgraded PLC4X dependencies from 0.9.0 to 0.13.1 in both app and library modules. Updated configuration files to use 'modbus-tcp' URL scheme. Refactored Plc4xDriver.kt to use new API methods and classes, including changes to connection management, tag addressing, and metadata capability checks to align with PLC4X 0.13.1.",
        "url": "https://github.com/vogler75/automation-gateway/commit/dc121a15d5d67d2f76d5dd8349c4a78671f5245a"
    },
    {
