        "email": "andreas.vogler@me.com",
        "date": "2025-11-25T21:01:47Z",
        "message": "Remove AI generated implementation plans.\n\nDeleted PHASE1_IMPLEMENTATION_STATUS.md and SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md, which contained detailed documentation and planning for JWT authentication and security improvements. This change may be part of a documentation cleanup or migration.",
