        "email": "andreas.vogler@me.com",
        "date": "2025-11-16T08:22:03Z",
        "message": "Add CLAUDE.md and update JSON schema title\n\nIntroduced a CLAUDE.md file with project guidance for Claude Code, including architecture, build commands, and configuration details. Also added a 'title' field to the yaml-json-schema.json for improved schema documentation.",
